Marketing Brief -- Paramount Communications Inc.:
   Firm's Unit Said Discussing
   Hiring Bernstein of Orion
Mr. Bernstein didn't return a telephone call, and
Paramount declined to comment.
   An Orion spokesman said Mr. Bernstein "has been contacted
by a number of companies. He has no contract or no deal with
anyone but Orion. He is trying to work out Orion's
difficulties right now."
   People familiar with the situation say Mr. Bernstein will
head all administrative, financial and business affairs for
the film and television units of Paramount and report
directly to Paramount Pictures Chairman Brandon Tartikoff.